A function bind together with its lexical scope bundled together is called closure.
simply Function apne aas pass k lexical scope ko yaad rakhte h jaha se wo aaye h loyal hote h 

************************EXAMPLE******************
function parent(){
    var name ="Vivek";
    
    function child(){
        console.log(name);
    }
    return child;
}
let z = parent();
z();



